            <para>
              <text>Clause 2(2) of Schedule 1 is amended by adding <amend.in quote="1">; and</amend.in> and also by adding the following paragraph:</text>
              <amend increment="1" quote="1">
                <label-para quote="1" skeleton="no">
                  <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes" quote="1">c</label>
                  <para>
                    <text>in the case of special resolutions required by section 106(1)(a) or (b), the right of a shareholder under section 110.</text>
                  </para>
